Once Upon A time, In a forest, there lived a monkey who resides on a berry tree which was on the banks of a river
In the Same Forest, there was a crocodile who lived on a rock which was on the banks of the river
One Day, came to the bank of the river, and asked the monkey to give him a berry
The monkey gave him a berry and asked the crocodile to eat it
The crocodile ate the berry and asked the monkey to give him another berry
Corcodile asked monkey to give him a ride on his back
Corcodile suddenly gobbled monkey up when monkey was looking at lush trees